{"tid":340494,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[請教]基金集中討論區","createTime":"2017-07-30T04:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T07:27:49.000Z","uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10e7474b0fa07ecd938b3049cdea2c25f6ecedc6","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"超級新手, 又見呢到好似無咩人會買基金咁,<br />\n其實有個少少既問題想請教一下, <br />\n如果係買股票基金既話, 連登仔當然會話, 屌啦直接買股票咪得囉,<br />\n利伸:我乜都未買, 不過就係想問下<br />\n假設有條友真係買左股票基金, 堆股票又真係升左, 又無派到息<br />\n咁條友係咪白買???<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢陣係贖得番自己買既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9b2bf4ca36508f8ed0179e2d435ecd198e88a2","tid":340494,"uid":44179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超級新手, 又見呢到好似無咩人會買基金咁,<br />\n其實有個少少既問題想請教一下, <br />\n如果係買股票基金既話, 連登仔當然會話, 屌啦直接買股票咪得囉,<br />\n利伸:我乜都未買, 不過就係想問下<br />\n假設有條友真係買左股票基金, 堆股票又真係升左, 又無派到息<br />\n咁條友係咪白買???<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢陣係贖得番自己買既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明你講乜，但基金都會有價格升跌，有啲基金會每月派息，同股票差不多"},{"pid":"58d48b2ff3814dfea29b774ec55774f9c2e4f675","tid":340494,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"買盈富啦"},{"pid":"aeaf776c9b28304ca3cb86f3af7c0f483f023835","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>超級新手, 又見呢到好似無咩人會買基金咁,<br />\n其實有個少少既問題想請教一下, <br />\n如果係買股票基金既話, 連登仔當然會話, 屌啦直接買股票咪得囉,<br />\n利伸:我乜都未買, 不過就係想問下<br />\n假設有條友真係買左股票基金, 堆股票又真係升左, 又無派到息<br />\n咁條友係咪白買???<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢陣係贖得番自己買既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明你講乜，但基金都會有價格升跌，有啲基金會每月派息，同股票差不多</blockquote><br />\n姐係話, 股票本身價格既升降係點樣係股票基金上反映出黎,<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知問得清唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33754e965fe8037f4aa3169ddbd219b661dab47c","tid":340494,"uid":74939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:37:16.000Z","msg":"基金留意年費、賳回費、表現收費。<br />\n如果買股票基金，又假設你識投資，不如自己買，<br />\n慳返唔洗比人賺，又flexible <br />\n<br />\n但真係要買股票fund，買2800啦，最平收費，<br />\n而家仲有好多etf，你有心就搵下資料，留意下收費。"},{"pid":"a5449713cc7295bdae5f8daa900d31cea0a36436","tid":340494,"uid":74939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>超級新手, 又見呢到好似無咩人會買基金咁,<br />\n其實有個少少既問題想請教一下, <br />\n如果係買股票基金既話, 連登仔當然會話, 屌啦直接買股票咪得囉,<br />\n利伸:我乜都未買, 不過就係想問下<br />\n假設有條友真係買左股票基金, 堆股票又真係升左, 又無派到息<br />\n咁條友係咪白買???<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢陣係贖得番自己買既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明你講乜，但基金都會有價格升跌，有啲基金會每月派息，同股票差不多</blockquote><br />\n姐係話, 股票本身價格既升降係點樣係股票基金上反映出黎,<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知問得清唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基金每日收市後，會更新每單位價格，<br />\n果時咪返映到<br />\n<br />\n而派息方面，睇基金既條款，<br />\n有一年派，有半年派，<br />\n有全派息，有不派息"},{"pid":"03160046417eb6dbd99108c4064c25ea90bbc032","tid":340494,"uid":74939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"Between 巴打點解買基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e7e84a26259a1f655ca2bbfd90e97a688687c3","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基金留意年費、賳回費、表現收費。<br />\n如果買股票基金，又假設你識投資，不如自己買，<br />\n慳返唔洗比人賺，又flexible <br />\n<br />\n但真係要買股票fund，買2800啦，最平收費，<br />\n而家仲有好多etf，你有心就搵下資料，留意下收費。</blockquote><br />\n我無打算買股票基金架, 叫做岩岩開始學投資(?) <br />\n同埋好奇先想問下"},{"pid":"fa0927a3d6c3508bf5a0a85e4a61b2ca74e2c639","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>超級新手, 又見呢到好似無咩人會買基金咁,<br />\n其實有個少少既問題想請教一下, <br />\n如果係買股票基金既話, 連登仔當然會話, 屌啦直接買股票咪得囉,<br />\n利伸:我乜都未買, 不過就係想問下<br />\n假設有條友真係買左股票基金, 堆股票又真係升左, 又無派到息<br />\n咁條友係咪白買???<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢陣係贖得番自己買既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明你講乜，但基金都會有價格升跌，有啲基金會每月派息，同股票差不多</blockquote><br />\n姐係話, 股票本身價格既升降係點樣係股票基金上反映出黎,<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知問得清唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基金每日收市後，會更新每單位價格，<br />\n果時咪返映到<br />\n<br />\n而派息方面，睇基金既條款，<br />\n有一年派，有半年派，<br />\n有全派息，有不派息</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦, 姐係話股票基金既價格理應係更加浮動啦, <br />\n同時基金公司都必須按合約同你贖回啦, 明白"},{"pid":"84f0488ecad907872399a5c3f1722bc9e49e6e02","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Between 巴打點解買基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識投資主要, meaning 對股票買賣係白紙一張,<br />\n只不過近排先係銀行開左個戶口想買啲基金(?)叫做投資下(?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56c4f54a8e646c35d4295d50e92b51d7ed012a0","tid":340494,"uid":74939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>超級新手, 又見呢到好似無咩人會買基金咁,<br />\n其實有個少少既問題想請教一下, <br />\n如果係買股票基金既話, 連登仔當然會話, 屌啦直接買股票咪得囉,<br />\n利伸:我乜都未買, 不過就係想問下<br />\n假設有條友真係買左股票基金, 堆股票又真係升左, 又無派到息<br />\n咁條友係咪白買???<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢陣係贖得番自己買既基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明你講乜，但基金都會有價格升跌，有啲基金會每月派息，同股票差不多</blockquote><br />\n姐係話, 股票本身價格既升降係點樣係股票基金上反映出黎,<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知問得清唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基金每日收市後，會更新每單位價格，<br />\n果時咪返映到<br />\n<br />\n而派息方面，睇基金既條款，<br />\n有一年派，有半年派，<br />\n有全派息，有不派息</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦, 姐係話股票基金既價格理應係更加浮動啦, <br />\n同時基金公司都必須按合約同你贖回啦, 明白</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以咁講<br />\n基金pool比你舊錢大好撚多<br />\n所買既股票同板塊多好多<br />\n可以更有效控制波幅<br />\n所以基金比股票價格唔會更浮動<br />\n<br />\n你第二句就正確"},{"pid":"965347e3ae3180eb57edc931591baa217982e385","tid":340494,"uid":74939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Between 巴打點解買基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識投資主要, meaning 對股票買賣係白紙一張,<br />\n只不過近排先係銀行開左個戶口想買啲基金(?)叫做投資下(?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奉勸你唔好咁認真研究銀行賣比你既基金<br />\nRetail bank 既fund 全部都係 垃 撚 圾<br />\n<br />\n如果係private bank 另計<br />\npb就多好多筍野<br />\n有時間真接學股票吧<br />\n<br />\nPs 巴打係米溝緊銀行個rm妹妹所以幫人買基金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82559b7277d08f6a27a8b2bb01ccf1e8364c5fa9","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Between 巴打點解買基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識投資主要, meaning 對股票買賣係白紙一張,<br />\n只不過近排先係銀行開左個戶口想買啲基金(?)叫做投資下(?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奉勸你唔好咁認真研究銀行賣比你既基金<br />\nRetail bank 既fund 全部都係 垃 撚 圾<br />\n<br />\n如果係private bank 另計<br />\npb就多好多筍野<br />\n有時間真接學股票吧<br />\n<br />\nPs 巴打係米溝緊銀行個rm妹妹所以幫人買基金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係, 不過都多謝你先, 我再睇睇到底係ETF(?得港交所有得睇), 抑或繼續上番個網搵基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0709fbaff36a58ed93fa5606b72a2019707a23cd","tid":340494,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"A random walk on wall street<br />\n絲打，可以睇睇e本書既中文版，用ETF indexing,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb2201ba8576d001d0f5f374bc36775e98f2787","tid":340494,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A random walk on wall street<br />\n絲打，可以睇睇e本書既中文版，用ETF indexing,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已DL, thank you very much<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}